OL,3,CBoy, 14, seriously injured in attack
OL,4,Cby two escaped dogs
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after a 14-
OL,7,Fyear-old boy was seriously injured in
OL,8,Fa dog attack in Wiltshire.
OL,10,FIt happened at around 9.30pm on
OL,11,FThursday (9 April), when the boy was
OL,12,Fattacked by two dogs who'd escaped
OL,13,Ffrom their property in Ryeleaze,
OL,14,FPotterne.
OL,16,FThe boy was taken to hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment to his injuries, which are
OL,18,Fnot thought to be life-changing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
