OL,3,CBoy, 14, seriously injured in attack
OL,4,Cby two escaped dogs
OL,6,FFollowing the attack, police officers
OL,7,Ffrom several units attended the scene
OL,8,Fand two dogs were seized.
OL,10,FThe owner of the dogs has been
OL,11,Fidentified and will be interviewed in
OL,12,Fconnection with the incident.
OL,14,FOfficers are still trying to identify
OL,15,Fthe breed of the dogs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
